215 288.1031 Florida Manufacturing Promotional Campaign.—
216 (1) The Legislature finds that there is a need for a
217 campaign to increase consumer awareness of manufacturing
218 activities in this state, to expand market exposure for
219 manufactured products and goods in this state, and to inspire
220 future generations of entrepreneurs, fabricators, and skilled
221 workers to build and grow domestic businesses and manufacturing
222 operations in this state. The Legislature further finds that a
223 campaign that creates a partnership between the state and
224 manufacturers in this state is necessary to promote and
225 advertise manufactured products efficiently.
